---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout 
	title="Locorda - Libraries for Privacy-Preserving Apps" 
	description="Dart libraries for powerful applications that respect data ownership. RDF toolkit, CRDT sync, and semantic web tools for modern development."
>
	<div class="hero-gradient">
		<div class="container">
			<div class="hero-content">
				<div class="hero-title">
					<img src="/logo-light.svg" alt="Locorda Logo" class="hero-logo" />
					<h1>Locorda</h1>
				</div>
				
				<p class="hero-tagline">
					Build <strong>powerful</strong> apps that respect <strong>data ownership</strong>
				</p>
				
				<p class="hero-description">
					Dart libraries combining semantic web standards (RDF) with offline-first sync ‚Äî<br/>
					enabling cloud-synced apps where <strong>users own their data</strong>.
				</p>
				
				<div class="hero-cta">
					<a href="#vision" class="cta-primary">Our Vision ‚Üí</a>
					<a href="/rdf/" class="cta-secondary">Explore RDF Libraries</a>
				</div>
			</div>
			
			<div class="blob blob-1"></div>
			<div class="blob blob-2"></div>
			<div class="blob blob-3"></div>
		</div>
	</div>
	
	<section id="vision" class="section vision-section">
		<div class="container vision-container">
			<div class="vision-personal">
				<img src="https://github.com/kkalass.png" alt="Klas Kala√ü" class="vision-avatar" />
				<div class="vision-personal-text">
					<h2>The Vision</h2>
					<p class="vision-byline">by Klas Kala√ü</p>
				</div>
			</div>
			
			<div class="vision-statement">
				<p class="vision-headline">
					What if apps were powerful <em>and</em> respected your data ownership?
				</p>
				
				<p class="vision-problem">
					Most applications today lock your data in proprietary formats and vendor-controlled servers. You can't easily export it, own it, or use it with other apps. The vendor controls access, privacy policies, and longevity.
				</p>
				
				<p class="vision-possibility">
					<strong>RDF and semantic web standards make building differently possible:</strong> Apps where <strong>you</strong> decide where data lives, who accesses it, and how it connects across applications ‚Äî without sacrificing modern features like cloud sync, collaboration, or rich UX.
				</p>
			</div>
			
			<div class="vision-principles">
				<div class="principle">
					<div class="principle-icon">üîê</div>
					<h3>User-Owned Data</h3>
					<p>Data lives where <strong>you</strong> choose ‚Äî your pod, your server, your rules. Not locked in vendor silos.</p>
				</div>
				
				<div class="principle">
					<div class="principle-icon">üîó</div>
					<h3>Semantic Interoperability</h3>
					<p>RDF's graph structure lets apps share and link data meaningfully, without tight coupling or data loss.</p>
				</div>
				
				<div class="principle">
					<div class="principle-icon">‚ö°</div>
					<h3>Developer-Friendly</h3>
					<p>Type-safe APIs, code generation, excellent IDE support. Semantic web shouldn't be painful to build.</p>
				</div>
				
				<div class="principle">
					<div class="principle-icon">üåê</div>
					<h3>Standards-Based</h3>
					<p>W3C standards (RDF 1.1, Turtle, JSON-LD) for long-term interoperability and vendor independence.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
			
			<div class="vision-inspiration">
				<p>
					These libraries power active projects in user-owned computing, including an <a href="/sync-engine/"><strong>alpha sync engine</strong></a> combining CRDTs with RDF for conflict-free synchronization. Drawing inspiration from <a href="https://solidproject.org/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>SOLID's vision</strong></a> of decentralized, user-controlled data.
				</p>
				<p class="vision-goal">
					<strong>The goal:</strong> Cloud-synced apps that are delightful to build and use ‚Äî <em>without</em> sacrificing data ownership.
				</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>
	
	<section class="section projects-section">
		<div class="container">
			<h2>Active Projects</h2>
			
			<div class="projects-grid">
				<a href="/rdf/" class="project-card project-card-featured">
					<div class="project-header">
						<div class="project-icon">üî∑</div>
						<span class="status-badge status-stable">‚úÖ Stable</span>
					</div>
					<h3>RDF Libraries</h3>
					<p class="project-tagline">Complete, type-safe RDF toolkit for Dart</p>
					<p class="project-description">
						Parse, serialize, query RDF data. Object mapping with code generation. Type-safe vocabularies for Schema.org, FOAF, and 30+ standards. W3C RDF 1.1 compliant.
					</p>
					<div class="project-features">
						<span class="feature-tag">Turtle</span>
						<span class="feature-tag">JSON-LD</span>
						<span class="feature-tag">RDF/XML</span>
						<span class="feature-tag">Type-Safe</span>
					</div>
				</a>
				
				<a href="/sync-engine/" class="project-card">
					<div class="project-header">
						<div class="project-icon">üîÑ</div>
						<span class="status-badge status-alpha">‚öóÔ∏è Alpha</span>
					</div>
					<h3>Sync Engine</h3>
					<p class="project-tagline">Offline-first sync with CRDTs + RDF</p>
					<p class="project-description">
						Experimental conflict-free synchronization for Flutter apps. Combines CRDT algorithms with RDF for semantic conflict resolution across SOLID pods and cloud services.
					</p>
					<div class="project-features">
						<span class="feature-tag">CRDTs</span>
						<span class="feature-tag">Offline-First</span>
						<span class="feature-tag">SOLID</span>
					</div>
				</a>
				
				<div class="project-card project-card-future">
					<div class="project-header">
						<div class="project-icon">üí¨</div>
						<span class="status-badge status-planned">üöß Planned</span>
					</div>
					<h3>Chat Essence</h3>
					<p class="project-tagline">Matrix conversations with AI insights</p>
					<p class="project-description">
						Browse Matrix chat with LLM-generated summaries, topic extraction, and daily/weekly briefings. Stay connected without notification overload.
					</p>
					<div class="project-features">
						<span class="feature-tag">Matrix</span>
						<span class="feature-tag">AI Summaries</span>
						<span class="feature-tag">Topics</span>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
	/* Hero Section */
	.hero-gradient {
		position: relative;
		background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2563eb 0%, #7c3aed 50%, #0891b2 100%);
		padding: 8rem 0;
		overflow: hidden;
	}
	
	.hero-content {
		position: relative;
		z-index: 10;
		text-align: center;
		color: white;
		max-width: 900px;
		margin: 0 auto;
	}
	
	.hero-title {
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: center;
		gap: 1.5rem;
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
	}
	
	.hero-logo {
		width: 100px;
		height: 100px;
	}
	
	.hero-content h1 {
		color: white;
		margin-bottom: 0;
		font-size: 3.5rem;
	}
	
	.hero-tagline {
		font-size: 2rem;
		line-height: 1.3;
		color: #ffffff;
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
		font-weight: 600;
	}
	
	.hero-description {
		font-size: 1.25rem;
		line-height: 1.6;
		color: #e0e7ff;
		margin-bottom: 3rem;
		font-weight: 300;
	}
	
	.hero-description strong {
		font-weight: 600;
		color: #ffffff;
	}
	
	.hero-cta {
		display: flex;
		gap: 1rem;
		justify-content: center;
		flex-wrap: wrap;
	}
	
	.cta-primary,
	.cta-secondary {
		display: inline-block;
		padding: 1.125rem 2.75rem;
		border-radius: 0.75rem;
		font-weight: 600;
		text-decoration: none;
		transition: all 0.2s ease;
		font-size: 1.125rem;
	}
	
	.cta-primary {
		background: white;
		color: #1e40af;
		box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.25);
	}
	
	.cta-primary:hover {
		background: #e0e7ff;
		transform: translateY(-2px);
		box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.35);
	}
	
	.cta-secondary {
		background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12);
		color: white;
		border: 2px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.4);
		backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
	}
	
	.cta-secondary:hover {
		background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.22);
		border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);
		transform: translateY(-2px);
	}
	
	/* Animated Blobs */
	.blob {
		position: absolute;
		border-radius: 50%;
		filter: blur(60px);
		opacity: 0.7;
		animation: float 25s infinite;
		mix-blend-mode: screen;
	}
	
	.blob-1 {
		width: 600px;
		height: 600px;
		background: radial-gradient(circle, #22d3ee 0%, transparent 60%);
		top: -15%;
		left: -15%;
		animation-delay: 0s;
	}
	
	.blob-2 {
		width: 500px;
		height: 500px;
		background: radial-gradient(circle, #c084fc 0%, transparent 60%);
		bottom: -15%;
		right: -15%;
		animation-delay: -8s;
	}
	
	.blob-3 {
		width: 450px;
		height: 450px;
		background: radial-gradient(circle, #818cf8 0%, transparent 60%);
		top: 40%;
		left: 60%;
		animation-delay: -16s;
	}
	
	@keyframes float {
		0%, 100% {
			transform: translate(0, 0) scale(1);
		}
		33% {
			transform: translate(30px, -30px) scale(1.1);
		}
		66% {
			transform: translate(-20px, 20px) scale(0.9);
		}
	}
	
	/* Vision Section */
	.vision-section {
		background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fafafa 0%, #f5f5f5 100%);
		padding: 6rem 2rem;
		margin: 0;
	}
	
	.vision-container {
		max-width: 900px;
		margin: 0 auto;
	}
	
	.vision-personal {
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: center;
		gap: 1.5rem;
		margin-bottom: 3rem;
	}
	
	.vision-avatar {
		width: 90px;
		height: 90px;
		border-radius: 50%;
		border: 4px solid #3b82f6;
		box-shadow: 0 6px 16px rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.25);
	}
	
	.vision-personal-text h2 {
		margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
		font-size: 2.5rem;
		color: #0f172a;
	}
	
	.vision-byline {
		color: #64748b;
		font-size: 1.125rem;
		margin: 0;
		font-style: italic;
	}
	
	.vision-statement {
		margin-bottom: 3rem;
	}
	
	.vision-headline {
		font-size: 2rem;
		line-height: 1.4;
		text-align: center;
		color: #0f172a;
		font-weight: 600;
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
	}
	
	.vision-headline em {
		color: #3b82f6;
		font-style: normal;
	}
	
	.vision-problem,
	.vision-possibility {
		font-size: 1.25rem;
		line-height: 1.7;
		color: #475569;
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
		text-align: center;
	}
	
	.vision-possibility strong {
		color: #0f172a;
		font-weight: 600;
	}
	
	.vision-principles {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
		gap: 2.5rem;
		margin: 4rem 0;
	}
	
	.principle {
		text-align: center;
	}
	
	.principle-icon {
		font-size: 3rem;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
	}
	
	.principle h3 {
		font-size: 1.25rem;
		margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
		color: #0f172a;
	}
	
	.principle p {
		color: #64748b;
		line-height: 1.6;
		font-size: 0.95rem;
	}
	
	.vision-inspiration {
		margin-top: 3rem;
		padding: 2rem;
		background: white;
		border-radius: 1rem;
		border: 2px solid #e5e7eb;
	}
	
	.vision-inspiration p {
		font-size: 1.05rem;
		line-height: 1.7;
		color: #475569;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
	}
	
	.vision-inspiration a {
		color: #3b82f6;
		font-weight: 600;
		text-decoration: none;
		border-bottom: 2px solid transparent;
		transition: border-color 0.2s;
	}
	
	.vision-inspiration a:hover {
		border-color: #3b82f6;
	}
	
	.vision-goal {
		font-style: italic;
		color: #64748b;
	}
	
	.vision-goal strong {
		color: #0f172a;
		font-weight: 600;
	}
	
	/* Projects Section */
	.projects-section {
		background: white;
	}
	
	.projects-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(320px, 1fr));
		gap: 2rem;
		margin-top: 3rem;
	}
	
	.project-card {
		background: white;
		border: 2px solid #e5e7eb;
		border-radius: 1rem;
		padding: 2rem;
		transition: all 0.3s;
		text-decoration: none;
		color: inherit;
		display: block;
		position: relative;
	}
	
	.project-card:hover {
		transform: translateY(-6px);
		box-shadow: 0 16px 40px rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.2);
		border-color: #3b82f6;
	}
	
	.project-card-featured {
		border-color: #3b82f6;
		background: linear-gradient(135deg, #eff6ff 0%, #ffffff 100%);
	}
	
	.project-card-future {
		opacity: 0.7;
		border-style: dashed;
		pointer-events: none;
	}
	
	.project-card-future:hover {
		transform: none;
		box-shadow: none;
		border-color: #e5e7eb;
	}
	
	.project-header {
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: space-between;
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
	}
	
	.project-icon {
		font-size: 2rem;
		line-height: 1;
		flex-shrink: 0;
	}
	
	.project-card h3 {
		font-size: 1.75rem;
		margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
		color: #0f172a;
	}
	
	.project-tagline {
		font-size: 1.25rem;
		color: #3b82f6;
		font-weight: 700;
		margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
	}
	
	.project-description {
		color: #64748b;
		line-height: 1.5;
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
		font-size: 0.95rem;
	}
	
	.project-features {
		display: flex;
		flex-wrap: wrap;
		gap: 0.5rem;
	}
	
	.feature-tag {
		background: #f1f5f9;
		color: #475569;
		padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
		border-radius: 9999px;
		font-size: 0.9rem;
		font-weight: 500;
	}
	
	.status-badge {
		display: inline-block;
		padding: 0.375rem 1rem;
		border-radius: 9999px;
		font-size: 0.875rem;
		font-weight: 600;
		color: white;
	}
	
	.status-stable {
		background: linear-gradient(135deg, #10b981 0%, #059669 100%);
	}
	
	.status-alpha {
		background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f59e0b 0%, #d97706 100%);
	}
	
	.status-planned {
		background: linear-gradient(135deg, #64748b 0%, #475569 100%);
	}
	
	/* Responsive */
	@media (max-width: 768px) {
		.hero-gradient {
			padding: 5rem 0;
		}
		
		.hero-logo {
			width: 70px;
			height: 70px;
		}
		
		.hero-content h1 {
			font-size: 2.5rem;
		}
		
		.hero-tagline {
			font-size: 1.5rem;
		}
		
		.hero-description {
			font-size: 1.125rem;
		}
		
		.vision-section {
			padding: 4rem 1.5rem;
		}
		
		.vision-headline {
			font-size: 1.5rem;
		}
		
		.vision-problem,
		.vision-possibility {
			font-size: 1.125rem;
		}
		
		.projects-grid {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
		}
		
		.vision-principles {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
			gap: 2rem;
		}
	}
</style>
